<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="hero-card rise-enter">
    <view class="hero-layout">
      <view class="hero-copy">
        <view class="hero-eyebrow">
          <text>CONTROL ROOM</text>
          <text>后台工作台</text>
        </view>
        <view class="hero-title">把后台也做得像产品，而不是临时工具箱。</view>
        <view class="hero-subtitle">这里统一承接菜谱维护、系统检测和高风险数据操作，让管理流程也有稳定清晰的节奏。</view>
        <view class="hero-metrics">
          <view class="hero-metric">
            <text class="hero-metric-value">{{stats.totalRecipes}}</text>
            <text class="hero-metric-label">总菜谱数</text>
          </view>
          <view class="hero-metric">
            <text class="hero-metric-value">{{stats.totalCategories}}</text>
            <text class="hero-metric-label">分类数量</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-side">
        <view class="hero-side-card">
          <text class="hero-side-label">REVIEW</text>
          <text class="hero-side-value">{{stats.pendingImports}}</text>
          <text class="hero-side-meta">待审核导入草稿，适合今天优先处理。</text>
        </view>
        <view class="hero-side-card">
          <text class="hero-side-label">FOCUS</text>
          <text class="hero-side-value">{{stats.featuredRecipes}}</text>
          <text class="hero-side-meta">近期重点内容，方便你快速回看当前更新节奏。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell fade-enter">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">CONTENT OPS</text>
        <text class="section-title">菜谱维护</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">常用动作放在同一屏，新增和管理不再来回找入口。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="lux-divider"></view>
    <view class="console-grid two-col">
      <view class="console-card accent-card" bindtap="goToRecipeManage">
        <text class="console-tag">MANAGE</text>
        <text class="console-title">菜谱管理</text>
        <text class="console-desc">查看菜谱列表、筛选、删除，并持续整理已有内容。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="console-card mint-card" bindtap="goToRecipeAdd">
        <text class="console-tag">CREATE</text>
        <text class="console-title">新增菜谱</text>
        <text class="console-desc">通过完整录入表单补充新内容，让后台录入也更像正式编辑器。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="console-card neutral-card" bindtap="goToRecipeImport">
        <text class="console-tag">IMPORT</text>
        <text class="console-title">导入助手</text>
        <text class="console-desc">先导入第三方原始内容，再人工审核后正式入库。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell fade-enter">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">SYSTEM</text>
        <text class="section-title">系统操作</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">先检测，再初始化，避免后台操作都像盲开开关。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="console-grid two-col">
      <view class="console-card neutral-card" bindtap="testConnection">
        <text class="console-tag">CHECK</text>
        <text class="console-title">测试连接</text>
        <text class="console-desc">验证云函数和数据接口是否在线，方便排查环境问题。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="console-card neutral-card" bindtap="initData">
        <text class="console-tag">SETUP</text>
        <text class="console-title">初始化数据</text>
        <text class="console-desc">快速恢复一套可演示、可联调的基础数据环境。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell fade-enter">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">DANGER ZONE</text>
        <text class="section-title">高风险操作</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">把危险操作单独隔离，避免误触和视觉混淆。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="danger-stack">
      <view class="danger-item" bindtap="clearData">
        <text class="danger-title">清空全部数据</text>
        <text class="danger-desc">删除菜谱、分类、收藏和评分数据。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="danger-item" bindtap="clearRecipes">
        <text class="danger-title">仅清空菜谱</text>
        <text class="danger-desc">保留分类和其它统计，只移除菜谱内容。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="danger-item" bindtap="clearCategories">
        <text class="danger-title">仅清空分类</text>
        <text class="danger-desc">适合重做分类体系时使用。</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card section-shell fade-enter">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title-wrap">
        <text class="section-kicker">ACTIVITY</text>
        <text class="section-title">系统日志</text>
        <text class="section-subtitle">保留最近的操作记录，方便回看刚刚做过什么。</text>
      </view>
      <view class="ghost-btn action-pill" bindtap="refreshLogs">刷新</view>
    </view>
    <view class="log-list" wx:if="{{logs.length > 0}}">
      <view class="log-item" wx:for="{{logs}}" wx:key="index">
        <text class="log-time">{{item.time}}</text>
        <text class="log-message {{item.type}}">{{item.message}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="empty-panel" wx:else>
      <text class="empty-title">暂无日志</text>
      <text class="empty-desc">执行一次后台动作后，这里会自动更新。</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
